GUIDES GO DESIGN SYSTEM - QUICK REFERENCE
COLORS
Primary: Forest Green (#2A5A3B), Sunset Orange (#FF6B35), Mountain Gray (#2D3142)
Secondary: Sky Blue (#7DCFFF), Earth Brown (#8B6B4A), White (#FFFFFF)
Utility: Success (#34C759), Warning (#FFB800), Error (#FF3B30), Info (#007AFF)
TYPOGRAPHY
Headings: Montserrat (48/36/24/20px)
Body: Inter (18/16/14px)
Base: 16px/24px
SPACING
Base unit: 8px
Scale: 4px → 64px (xs to 3xl)
BREAKPOINTS
Mobile: 320px
Tablet: 768px
Desktop: 1024px
Wide: 1200px+
KEY COMPONENTS

Buttons: Orange bg/White text (Primary), Green border/transparent bg (Secondary)
Cards: White bg, 12px radius, subtle shadow
Nav: 72px height, sticky, white bg
Icons: 24x24px, rounded style

ANIMATIONS
Transitions: 0.2-0.5s ease
Hover: Scale 1.02 on cards
Scroll: Smooth parallax effects